{"tid":987970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10 年挑戰掀熱潮，專家：Facebook 恐別有用心","createTime":"2019-01-19T16:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T17:19:57.000Z","uid":212399,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"359776d0140efa2fdbccdbe4842b9502ebc71df9","tid":987970,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/15125129/shutterstock_558937273-e1497585874665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F15125129%2Fshutterstock_558937273-e1497585874665.jpg&h=8e54578e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「10 年挑戰」（#10YearChallenge）最近在 Facebook 等社群媒體掀起風潮，網友紛紛貼出自己 10 年前後對比照。專家猜測 Facebook 暗中推波助瀾是為收集臉部數據，研發「臉部辨識演算法」。<br />\nFacebook 16 日和這項活動保持距離，不過儘管 Facebook 否認別有用心，研究社群媒體公司的專家不排除這個可能性。<br />\n紐約大學史登商學院（Stern School of Business）教授韋柏（Amy Webb）表示，這項照片挑戰給予 Facebook 「機器學習」的絕佳機會。<br />\n她告訴哥倫比亞廣播公司新聞網（CBS News）：「它提供 Facebook 學習、訓練他們的系統，以更佳辨識細微變化的絕佳機會。」<br />\n（譯者：陳政一；首圖來源：shutterstock）<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/01/19/10-year-challenge-facebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F01%2F19%2F10-year-challenge-facebook%2F&d=YgW4bJlYVUOjhiEhYnE5HgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c7ade707\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/01/19/10-year-challenge-facebook/</a>"},{"pid":"06e2e52f9de624c2a5f0dff681375f42d1aedf29","tid":987970,"uid":1267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6b0d9dcd8c90783d415961d4f49dda57b605bc","tid":987970,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21b0a7a2154467170bfee523162ba27c18